The evidence with the title 'Senate majority leader McConnell: ObamaCare failed Americans ... ' says Jan 9, 2017  ... By nearly any measure, ObamaCare has failed: it didn't lower costs, it didn't increase choice, middle-class families continue to lose health plans They  ... Will be a stable transition period, and once repeal is passed we will turn to replacement policies that cost less and work better than what we have now. 
